title: Star Ocean 3: Till the End of Time Walkthrough (pdf)
description:
This is a torrent I found on Torrent Reactor.  After searching The Pirate Bay and coming up with nothing, I had to turn to other sources.

At 133 MB this scan of the actual walkthrough is quite large, yet it works well for me.  I use Document Reader on Ubuntu.

Enjoy this, my first torrent upload to The Pirate Bay!  If anything else of interest is found I'll be sure to upload it!  Let me know if anybody has any issues...
